<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>SparkCode</title>

  <!-- Bootstrap -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

  <!-- CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">

  <!-- Ícones -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.css">

  <style>
    body {
      background-color: black;
      color: aliceblue;
    }

    h1 {
      color: aliceblue;
    }

    p {
      text-align: center;
      color: aliceblue;
    }

    .netflix {
      background-color: aliceblue;
      padding: 15px 20px 25px 35px;
      margin: 10px 85vh 80px 50px;
      color: black;
      border-radius: 80px 25px 35px 100px;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: scale(1.03);
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .cc {
      margin: 15px;
    }

    .card p {
      color: #444;
    }

    .plan-card{
background: linear-gradient(135deg,#111,#000);
border-radius:20px;
width:350px;
color:white;
box-shadow:0px 0px 20px rgba(255,0,0,0.4);
}

.plan-card h3{
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.preco{
font-size:45px;
color:#ff2c2c;
}

.btn-assinar{
background:#ff2c2c;
color:white;
border:none;
padding:10px 25px;
border-radius:8px;
}

.btn-assinar:hover{
background:#ff0000;
transform:scale(1.05);
transition:0.3s;
}
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <!-- NAVBAR -->
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-black">
    <div class="container">

      <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
        <h1>CodeSpark</h1>
      </a>

      <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#menu">
        <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
      </button>

      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="menu">
      <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">

  <li class="nav-item">
    <a class="nav-link" href="/">Cadastro</a>
  </li>
<li class="nav-item">
  <a class="nav-link" href="/login-exclusivo">Login Premium</a>
</li>

  <li class="nav-item">
    <a class="nav-link" href="#">Sobre nós</a>
  </li>

  <li class="nav-item">
    <a class="nav-link" href="#">Serviços</a>
  </li>

  <li class="nav-item">
    <a class="nav-link" href="#">Contato</a>
  </li>

</ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </nav>


  <!-- DESCRIÇÃO -->
  <p>
    Desenvolvemos soluções digitais para empresas e projetos modernos.
    Sites profissionais, sistemas web e suporte tecnológico.
  </p>


  <!-- SERVIÇOS -->
  <div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row g-4">

      <!-- NETFLIX -->
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card p-4 h-100 shadow" style="border-radius:20px;">

          <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/08/Netflix_2015_logo.svg"
            style="width:120px; margin-bottom:15px;">

          <div class="row align-items-center">

            <div class="col-6">
              <img
                src="https://assets.nflxext.com/ffe/siteui/vlv3/eb110559-67e9-40ec-8f1c-4a45b9f9c9bb/web/BR-pt-20260309-TRIFECTA-perspective_2f6868b1-a3e4-4913-aa51-6915b914c4aa_large.jpg"
                class="img-fluid">
            </div>

            <div class="col-6">
              <p>Filmes, séries e produções originais exclusivas da Netflix.</p>

              <h5 style="color:#E50914;">R$ 39,90 / mês</h5>

              <button class="btn" style="background:#E50914; color:white;">
                Assinar
              </button>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>


      <!-- APPLE TV+ -->
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card p-4 h-100 shadow" style="border-radius:20px;">

          <img src="https://cdn.worldvectorlogo.com/logos/apple-tv-plus-logo.svg"
            style="width:120px; margin-bottom:15px;">

          <div class="row align-items-center">

            <div class="col-6">
              <img
                src="https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Features221/v4/90/55/5f/90555fe3-c853-d69d-500e-13209344f1c8/a058fec-8e41-4f1a-902d-82dd886f5af4.png/2160x3839sr.webp"
                class="img-fluid">
            </div>

            <div class="col-6">
              <p>Séries e filmes originais da Apple com alta qualidade e produções premiadas.</p>

              <h5 style="color:black;">R$ 21,90 / mês</h5>

              <button class="btn" style="background:black; color:white;">
                Assinar
              </button>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>


      <!-- DISNEY+ -->
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card p-4 h-100 shadow" style="border-radius:20px;">

          <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3e/Disney%2B_logo.svg"
            style="width:120px; margin-bottom:15px;">

          <div class="row align-items-center">

            <div class="col-6">
              <img
                src="https://disney.images.edge.bamgrid.com/ripcut-delivery/v2/variant/disney/0736EF496F9FDC08ABE3EFC804F2D887F76441C014894E4CD00E389019949BF5/compose?format=webp&width=1536"
                class="img-fluid">
            </div>

            <div class="col-6">
              <p>Filmes da Disney, Marvel, Star Wars e Pixar.</p>

              <h5 style="color:#113CCF;">R$ 33,90 / mês</h5>

              <button class="btn" style="background:#113CCF; color:white;">
                Assinar
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
 
  <div class="container mt-5 mb-5">

    <div class="text-center mb-4">
      <h2>Plano CodeSpark</h2>
      <p>Acesse os principais streamings pagando apenas um valor.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">

      <div class="plan-card text-center p-5">

        <h3>Plano Completo</h3>

        <p>
          Com a CodeSpark você tem acesso aos principais serviços de streaming
          em um único plano simples.
        </p>

        <h1 class="preco">R$ 39,90</h1>
        <span>/ mês</span>

        <br><br>

       <a href="/login" class="btn btn-lg btn-assinar">
Assinar agora
</a>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</body>

</html>